nodes.text: This Mon Calamari lived on the ocean-covered planet of Dac in the Mon Calamari capital city during the Battle of Mon Cala around 21 BBY.
During the Battle of Mon Cala, this Mon Calamari soldier helped fight off the Quarren and the Separatist Aqua droids.

At one point during the battle, this soldier along with three others discovered Prince Lee-Char and padawan Ahsoka Tano hiding inside a tunnel which was under attack from Separatist commander Riff Tamson, who was trying to break inside. This soldier and the rest of the squad then began firing at Tamson, but with no effect as the karkarodon quickly turned around and killed the whole squad, including this soldier, though it gave the prince enough time to escape.
The soldier first appeared in the Star Wars: The Clone Wars TV series season four episode Water War and was voiced by Corey Burton.
